Package tetrisgame

package tetrisgame
  • Class
    Description
    Coord
    Represents a coordinate point on a grid
    GameFrame
    The main frame of the Tetris game.
    PauseMenu
    The PauseMenu class represents a menu that appears when the game is paused.
    StartWindow
    The StartWindow class serves as the entry point for the Tetris game.
    TetrisHUD
    TetrisHUD is a graphical component that displays the current game status, including the score and a preview of the next tetromino to the current Game window GameFrame
    TetrisPanel
    The TetrisPanel class represents the game board for a Tetris game.
    TetrisSquare
    Represents a single square in the Tetris game grid.
    TetrisUtils
    Utility class for managing Tetris game constants and utility methods.
    TetrisUtils.ShapeType
    Enum representing the types of Tetris shapes.
    Tetromino
    Represents a Tetromino, the main building block of Tetris gameplay.
    TetroShape
    Represents the shape of a Tetromino in the Tetris game.
